  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们来梳理一下智慧教育系统的数据流转。核心是学生数据库，但里面还嵌套了内容分发和课堂服务，我想把这三个放在一个大的ROS2集群里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，ROS2作为顶层子图，内部包含C1学生数据库、C2内容CDN和C3课堂服务。那C3课堂服务本身是不是还需要再展开一层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C3",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "HWI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，C3课堂服务里面要挂一个SI，也就是LMS门户，作为师生统一入口。这个SI同时属于HWI子图。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "HWI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，HWI子图已创建，内部放置SI节点标注为Education_LMS_Portal。接下来SI往下还要连什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "SI",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SI作为中枢，要双向同步三个成绩相关的模块。我打算把M1、M2、M3都放在Hardware子图里，分别对应成绩同步和学生库的不同实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SI",
        "Hardware",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：M1和M2都是GradeSync，M3是StudentDB？这三个都要和SI双向连接？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3",
        "SI",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，双向箭头。另外上面C1、C2、C3都要单向指向SI，表示数据上报到LMS门户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Hardware子图已建，M1、M2、M3放入其中。C1→SI、C2→SI、C3→SI的单向连线已完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hardware",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说C3在ROS2里，但C3本身又是ClassroomService，而HWI子图的标题也是ClassroomService，这里会不会重复？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C3",
        "HWI",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "确实，HWI子图的标签我先用Education_ClassroomService，但内部实际放的是SI（LMS_Portal）。这样HWI代表的是课堂服务层，而ROS2里的C3是具体的课堂服务节点，层级不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HWI",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "SI",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以这么理解。那Hardware子图的标题呢？我原本想叫LMS_Portal，但SI已经是LMS_Portal了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hardware",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "SI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Hardware子图我标注为Education_LMS_Portal，作为硬件基础设施层，里面承载M1、M2、M3三个数据同步组件。这样三层结构：ROS2（数据服务层）→ HWI（课堂服务层）→ Hardware（硬件基础设施层）。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hardware",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "ROS2",
        "HWI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "层级清晰了。不过ROS2子图的标题我确认一下，应该叫Education_StudentDB，因为C1是核心，C2和C3围绕它展开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整：ROS2子图标题改为Education_StudentDB，HWI为Education_ClassroomService，Hardware为Education_LMS_Portal。三层架构现在对齐了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "HWI",
        "Hardware",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "SI和M1、M2、M3的双向箭头是实线还是虚线？成绩同步需要强调实时性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "目前用的是实线双向箭头（<--），符合实时同步的语义。C1、C2、C3到SI是单向实线（--），表示上报。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "M3",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "M3我标注的是Education_StudentDB，但它和C1的StudentDB是什么关系？M3是硬件层的本地缓存实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "M3",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "C1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解，C1是中心库，M3是边缘节点缓存，通过SI双向同步。这样架构支持离线场景，M1、M2作为GradeSync负责成绩数据的双向流动。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "M3",
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "C2的ContentCDN只连SI吗？不需要直接连Hardware层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C2",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "SI",
        "Hardware"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "按当前设计，C2只单向指向SI，内容分发通过SI中转。如果CDN要直推边缘，可以后续扩展。目前保持三层解耦。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C2",
        "SI",
        "Hardware"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "整体结构确认了。ROS2层：StudentDB为核心，搭配CDN和ClassroomService；HWI层：LMS_Portal作为统一入口；Hardware层：GradeSync双节点加StudentDB边缘缓存。全部通过SI中枢互联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ROS2",
        "HWI",
        "Hardware",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "SI",
        "M1",
        "M2",
